Inspect the file with cat /etc/apt/sources.list.d/docker.list 芒聙聰 it must be a single unbroken line; delete it with sudo rm /etc/apt/sources.list.d/docker.list and re-run the printf block.
Official reference: https://docs.docker.com/engine/install/ubuntu/
